reviewText: Is just basic Knowledge.  DON'T WASTE YOUR MONEY! !!!

This is my first time listening to Niurka.  I found her to be an excellent trainer/speaker.

The DVD is about 105 minutes long.  I found it to be insightful, educational, inspiring, and entertaining!  I already watched/listened to the DVD three different times.  My understanding of the subject (Supreme Influence) gets better each time.

I am glad I bought this DVD.

I am addicted to motivational training, and I know of Niurka because she worked with Tony Robbins. She has a great energetic style and lots of useful ideas about how to motivate ourselves and others through the language that we use. I have used several of her techniques in sales presentations, and I can tell you that this purchase has more than payed for itself.
